maps/tree-dng/f4/boss.json/entities/16/s.orig: One has reached the very top of Grand Krys'kajo.
maps/tree-dng/f4/boss.json/entities/16/s.text: Тот, кто достиг самой вершины Гранд Крис'кайо.

maps/tree-dng/f4/boss.json/entities/16/s.orig: Standing high above the earth, one is now ready.
maps/tree-dng/f4/boss.json/entities/16/s.text: Стоя высоко над землёй, он уже готов.

maps/tree-dng/f4/boss.json/entities/24/s.orig: One has fully ascended Krys'kajo and shown true mastery of Shock and Wave.
maps/tree-dng/f4/boss.json/entities/24/s.text: Тот, кто покорил Крис'кайо и показал истинное мастерство Шока и Волны.
